{"type":null,"faqId":19820,"title":"G7移动版手机待机状态解锁开屏，为什么手机蓝牙突然提示正在搜索（蓝牙我是一直开启的没关过，只是一直没连接），这样自己在我没有点击搜索的情况下自动运行，很不安全？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>晚上10点后至少一个小时以上灭屏，或0点后半小时以上灭屏，会关闭没有连接的WLAN和蓝牙，亮屏立即恢复原来状态,省电精灵有以上机制，所以出现以上情况，属于正常机制。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3160","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1423811149000,"seriesProductName":"G760-TL00","visitedTimes":84,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"G7移动版,待机,蓝牙,提示,搜索","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}